OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1780405872
OL,3,CFamily 'will never forgive' hospital
OL,4,Cfor 'avoidable' death of grandmother
OL,6,FThe death of a Turkish-speaking woman
OL,7,Fat a Birmingham hospital could have
OL,8,Fbeen avoided if she had been given an
OL,9,Finterpreter, according to the health
OL,10,Fwatchdog.
OL,12,FThe Parliamentary and Health Service
OL,13,FOmbudsman (PHSO) said that Sevinc
OL,14,FUlkueri died after doctors at
OL,15,FBirmingham Heartlands Hospital missed
OL,16,Fwarning signs of a bowel obstruction,
OL,17,Fand she was unable to communicate her
OL,18,Fpain.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
