CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1780405872
OL,3,CFamily 'will never forgive' hospital
OL,4,Cfor 'avoidable' death of grandmother
OL,6,FThe Trust has apologised to Sevinc's
OL,7,Ffamily, paid them #15,000 in
OL,8,Frecognition of the distress caused,
OL,9,Fand has agreed to improve its approach
OL,10,Fto investigating bowel problems.
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
